# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WealthRadar — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file → .env.local and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env.local to git (it's already in .gitignore).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Google OAuth 2.0 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# How to get:
#   1. https://console.cloud.google.com → New Project "WealthRadar"
#   2. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID
#   3. Application type: Web application
#   4. Authorised JavaScript origins:
#        http://localhost:3000
#        https://wealthradar.web.app
#        https://wealthradar.firebaseapp.com
#   5. Copy the Client ID here:
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID_HERE

# ── App Config ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_APP_NAME=WealthRadar
VITE_APP_VERSION=1.0.0
VITE_APP_URL=https://wealthradar.web.app
